Subject: [PATCH v5 20/21] media: videobuf2: Stop using internal dma-buf lock
Date: Tue, 13 Sep 2022 22:27:56 +0300
Message-Id: <20220913192757.37727-21-dmitry.osipenko@collabora.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.37.3
